title: Beautiful! Turn-Key Gasquet Home 170 Middle Fork Rd.,
text:
Beautiful! Turn-Key Gasquet Home 170 Middle Fork Rd., ad date: 10/10/2015 
Turn-Key Gasquet Home 170 Middle Fork Rd., Gasquet, CA Smith River front upscale home in Gasquet on the confluence of the North Fork and Middle Fork. Gated 1.39 acres with 300' of river frontage & 1,300 sq.ft. deck overlooking the incredible Smith River. Fully landscaped with electronic gate entry, this property features a year 'round stream that meanders throughout the property. 4 bed/3 bath, 3,375 sq.ft. Living room with fireplace, huge family room with river views & open floor design to accommodate any lifestyle. MLS# 1500353 $679,000 Donna Zorn, Agent 1000 Northcrest Dr., Crescent City 707-951-0857 or 464-9741, #01221233
